## Chart Repo

Add the following repo to use the chart:

```bash
helm repo add home-charts https://95gabor.github.io/home-charts
helm repo update
```

### Installation

- Install/upgrade in a namespace (using local chart directory):

```bash
helm upgrade --install {{ .Name }} . \
  -n {{ .Name }} --create-namespace \
  -f values.yaml
```

- Or install from a chart repository:

```bash
helm upgrade --install {{ .Name }} home-charts/{{ .Name }} \
  -n {{ .Name }} --create-namespace \
  -f values.yaml
```

- Uninstall:

```bash
helm uninstall {{ .Name }} -n {{ .Name }}
```

